comments: Ntilikina (DAL) places his hand on Holmes' (SAC) shoulder and Holmes briefly hooks Ntilikina's arm.
Porzingis (DAL) and Fox (SAC) make incidental contact with each other as the two players meet at the same point.
Bagley III (SAC) legally contests Brunson's (DAL) shot attempt at the rim.  Brunson extends his leg backwards and creates the marginal contact.
Fox (SAC) moves alongside of Brunson (DAL) and makes marginal contact that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Holmes (SAC) firms up in a screening position in the path of Ntilikina (DAL) and does not deliver contact.
Porzingis (DAL) moves forward into Holmes (SAC) but the contact prior to the blocked shot is marginal.
Fox (SAC) makes contact to Porzingis's (DAL) arms and affects his shot attempt in the post.
Finney-Smith (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position as he defends the drive to the basket and shot attempt by Barnes (SAC).
Holmes (SAC) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Fox (SAC) reaches in and makes clean contact with the ball and Barnes (SAC) legally contests the jump shot attempt by Porzingis (DAL).
Finney-Smith (DAL) makes contact to Haliburton's (SAC) arm to commit a take foul before he is in his upward shooting motion.
Ntilikina (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position defending the drive to the basket by Fox (SAC).
